<body><p><b> Human Rights Council  
</b></p>
<p><b>Decision 6/105. Report of the Preparatory Committee on the 
Durban Review Conference 
</b></p>
<p> At its 22nd meeting, on 28 September 2007, the Human Rights Council 
</p>
<p>decided, without a vote, to adopt the following: 
</p>
<p>&#8220;Recalling its resolution 3/2 of 8 December 2006, the Human Rights Council 
</p>
<p>invites the Preparatory Committee on the Durban Review Conference to submit its 
</p>
<p>reports to the General Assembly.&#8221; 
</p>
<p> 
</p>
